{"title":"北京的请柬——摘自一位新兵的信","authors":["王锦秋"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的请柬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——摘自一位新兵的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王锦秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一张像片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄给母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同装进信封的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有首都朗朗的天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈！这不是梦境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子寄给你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个温暖的北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在小镇唯一的摄影中心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总是让我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和画上的北京一起留影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，“小北京”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了我甜甜的乳名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈！我懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会用开花的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫这一片醉人的温馨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一张像片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈妈一生最出色的作品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！妈妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以北京的名义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你发出热情的邀请"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}